           ðŸ§ª Run code coverage test without checking test dependencies

         deploy_latest_doc
           ðŸš€ ðŸ“” Deploy Documentation Site To S3 as Latest Doc

         deploy_versioned_doc
           ðŸš€ ðŸ“” Deploy Documentation Site To S3 as Versioned Doc

         install
           ** ðŸ’¾ Install main dependencies and Package itself

         install_all
           ** ðŸ’¾ ðŸ’» ðŸ§ª ðŸ“” ðŸ¤– Install All Dependencies

